21#include "mpc-impl.h"
22
23int
24mpc_pow_fr (mpc_ptr z, mpc_srcptr x, mpfr_srcptr y, mpc_rnd_t rnd)
25{
26 mpc_t yy;
27 int inex;
28
29 /* avoid copying the significand of y by copying only the struct */
30 mpc_realref(yy)[0] = y[0];
31 mpfr_init2 (mpc_imagref(yy), MPFR_PREC_MIN);
32 mpfr_set_ui (mpc_imagref(yy), 0, MPFR_RNDN);
33 inex = mpc_pow (z, x, yy, rnd);
34 mpfr_clear (mpc_imagref(yy));
35 return inex;
36}
